g.text: Reported HCQ usage in early stages of Covid-19:
14 countries were excluded from this HCQ cross-country observational study, because their HCQ usage
is 'mixed'. The conclusions would not have changed if they had been left in as an intermediary
level of the intervention, but the HCQ effect would go away if some key categorisations had been
GDP per capita, HCQ use and Covid-19 death rates
Source: HCQ policy on usage, and death adjustment factors by diabetes, hypertension, gender and age, from an anonymous
article on the web, 'Early treatment with hydroxychloroquine'; Covid-19 death numbers from Our World in Data; population
and GDP from the World Bank World Development Indicators. Analysis by http://freerangestats.info.
